---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Klinis — Ninja Urban Farming" 
  description="Panduan diagnosis dan penanganan penyakit pada ikan lele dan tanaman urban farming."
>
  <header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>🏥 Klinis</h1>
      <p>Diagnosis cepat dan solusi praktis untuk masalah kesehatan tanaman dan ikan.</p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="card-grid">
        <div class="card clinic-card">
          <div class="clinic-icon">🐟</div>
          <h3>Klinis Lele</h3>
          <p>8 penyakit umum pada budidaya lele bioflok: gejala, penyebab, dan penanganan organik.</p>
          <ul class="clinic-list">
            <li>White Spot / Bintik Putih</li>
            <li>Columnaris / Fin Rot</li>
            <li>Jamur Air</li>
            <li>Septikemia Bakteri</li>
            <li>Kutu Jangkar</li>
            <li>Kutu Ikan</li>
            <li>Dropsy</li>
            <li>Sirip & Ekor Rusak</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/ninja-urban-farming/klinis/lele" class="btn">Buka Klinis Lele</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="card clinic-card">
          <div class="clinic-icon">🌿</div>
          <h3>Klinis Tanaman</h3>
          <p>6 masalah kesehatan tanaman urban farming: hama, jamur, dan gangguan fisiologis.</p>
          <ul class="clinic-list">
            <li>Layu Fusarium</li>
            <li>Busuk Daun & Bercak Daun</li>
            <li>Damping-Off</li>
            <li>Kutu Daun & Whitefly</li>
            <li>Ulat Kubis & Ulat Tanduk</li>
            <li>Blossom-End Rot</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/ninja-urban-farming/klinis/tanaman" class="btn">Buka Klinis Tanaman</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="emergency-card">
        <div class="emergency-icon">🚨</div>
        <div class="emergency-content">
          <h3>Ingat: Pencegahan Lebih Baik dari Pengobatan</h3>
          <p>Sebagian besar penyakit muncul karena kualitas air buruk, kepadatan tinggi, atau tanaman stres. Pantau sistemmu setiap hari, jaga kualitas air, dan deteksi dini.</p>
          <a href="/ninja-urban-farming/sop" class="btn">Lihat SOP Pencegahan</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .clinic-card {
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--color-primary-500);
  }
  
  .clinic-icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    background: var(--color-primary-50);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 0 auto 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .clinic-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .clinic-list li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
  
  .clinic-list li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  
  .clinic-list li::before {
    content: '•';
    color: var(--color-primary-500);
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .emergency-card {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef2f2 0%, #fee2e2 100%);
    border: 1px solid #fecaca;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }
  
  .emergency-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  
  .emergency-content h3 {
    color: #991b1b;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
  
  .emergency-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .emergency-card {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
      align-items: center;
    }
  }
</style>
